{
  "stem": "8569.4",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I-- indeed they did.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think that everybody who lost a family needed to replace it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Indeed, if you did not have a friend, you did not have a zeal for life.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I think that friendships and taking care of somebody other than yourself made a great deal of difference.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] Perhaps I could go back to the Lager B when we were transferred [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] to Lager A, which used to be men's lager before.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] We were told that we should volunteer for a-- as a metallurgist.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We didn't know what metallurgists were, but we decided we're going to be metallurgists.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My sister and I.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And as metallurgists, we were-- [PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] we were then scheduled to work.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What we didn't know but eventually knew-- that was a munition factory.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In the transfer from Lager A to Lager B, we were in a block whose Blockalteste, or responsible for the block, was a non-Jewish woman by the name of Maria, who eventually became a kapo of the camp.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "At that time, my sister became sick with typhoid.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] There was a kind of a hospital in the camp.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But anybody who was in the hospital was doomed and was taken to the gas right away.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So we decided not to let her go to the hospital.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And it so happened that there was a market in Birkenau.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "People, particularly the German prisoners, used to get parcels from home.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And after working between two blocks, they used to sell the goodies from their parcels for bread or soup.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
